<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 02:18:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>载有南卡罗来纳大学兄弟会的巴士在密西西比州发生翻车事故 11人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11-injured-as-bus-carrying-university-of-south-carolina-fraternity-crashes-in-mississippi/articleshow/109098641.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098641.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;密西西比州圣路易斯湾附近发生一起涉及南卡罗来纳大学学生的巴士事故，造成 11 人受伤。司机蒂娜·威尔逊和一名学生受重伤，其他人被送往医院。威尔逊的敏捷思维和学生保罗·克鲁恩的干预避免了一场潜在的灾难。该大学正在为受影响的学生提供支持。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 01:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/11-injured-as-bus-carrying-university-of-south-carolina-fraternity-crashes-in-mississippi/articleshow/109098641.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭黎巴嫩真主党训练营</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-conducts-air-strikes-on-hezbollah-training-camp-in-lebanon/articleshow/109098367.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098367.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列对黎巴嫩东部贝卡谷地的一个真主党训练营进行了空袭。真主党击落一架以色列无人机后，紧张局势升级。巴勒贝克附近的萨弗里镇遭到袭击，没有人员伤亡报告。真主党证实了无人机被击落的消息，并强调了持续的敌对行动。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:48:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-conducts-air-strikes-on-hezbollah-training-camp-in-lebanon/articleshow/109098367.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗发生4.3级地震</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/earthquake-of-magnitude-4-3-strikes-afghanistan/articleshow/109098039.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109098039.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 00:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/earthquake-of-magnitude-4-3-strikes-afghanistan/articleshow/109098039.cms</guid></item><item><title>“继续支持以色列”：苏纳克表示以色列与哈马斯的冲突“必须结束”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/continue-to-stand-by-israel-sunak-says-israel-hamas-conflict-must-end/articleshow/109097369.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109097369.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克支持以色列与哈马斯的冲突，呼吁结束暴力并释放人质。敦促加沙人道主义暂停，提及伤亡情况，并强调英国公众情绪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:30:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/continue-to-stand-by-israel-sunak-says-israel-hamas-conflict-must-end/articleshow/109097369.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国难民署呼吁提供 6.2 亿美元支持伊朗和巴基斯坦的阿富汗移民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/unhcr-appeals-for-usd-620-million-to-support-afghan-migrants-in-iran-and-pakistan/articleshow/109097042.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109097042.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国难民署呼吁提供 6.2 亿美元援助伊朗和巴基斯坦境内的阿富汗移民，以应对阿富汗的严峻形势。该报告预计到 2024 年将向 480 万阿富汗移民和 250 万收容社区成员提供援助，并强调迫切需要人道主义援助来帮助 2,370 万人生存。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:03:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/unhcr-appeals-for-usd-620-million-to-support-afghan-migrants-in-iran-and-pakistan/articleshow/109097042.cms</guid></item><item><title>彼得·佩莱格里尼赢得斯洛伐克总统选举</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-wins-slovakia-presidential-elections/articleshow/109096954.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096954.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在斯洛伐克，彼得·佩莱格里尼 (Peter Pellegrini) 以 53% 的支持率击败伊万·科尔科克 (Ivan Korcok) 的 47% 赢得总统选举。科尔科克优雅地认输，强调对结果的尊重。这次选举的焦点是对乌克兰冲突的不同看法，佩莱格里尼主张和谈。这场胜利反映了斯洛伐克在战争和外交上的立场。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 23:05:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-wins-slovakia-presidential-elections/articleshow/109096954.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国对阿富汗妇女和儿童营养不良激增发出警告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-raises-alarm-on-surging-malnutrition-in-afghan-women-and-children/articleshow/109096386.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096386.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国世界粮食计划署驻阿富汗办事处对妇女和儿童营养不良率不断上升表示担忧，喀布尔的营养不良病例在三年内增加了两倍。人道主义援助的减少加剧了这一问题，影响了营养不良患者的心理健康和设施。贫困、不安全和塔利班的限制使局势进一步恶化。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:39:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/un-raises-alarm-on-surging-malnutrition-in-afghan-women-and-children/articleshow/109096386.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争已持续半年，特拉维夫爆发针对内塔尼亚胡的大规模抗议活动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/massive-protests-in-tel-aviv-against-netanyahu-as-gaza-war-reaches-half-year-mark/articleshow/109096032.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109096032.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着加沙冲突进入第七个月，数万名以色列人在特拉维夫抗议，要求举行选举并要求内塔尼亚胡辞职。反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德批评领导层。据报道发生了冲突，并逮捕了一人。加沙人质家属参加示威，军队打捞第十二具人质尸体。冲突造成的死亡人数：加沙超过 33,000 人死亡，129 名人质幸存。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/massive-protests-in-tel-aviv-against-netanyahu-as-gaza-war-reaches-half-year-mark/articleshow/109096032.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰总统泽连斯基警告俄罗斯袭击导致防空能力不足</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-warns-of-air-defence-shortage-amid-russian-attacks/articleshow/109095807.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095807.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰总统泽连斯基对俄罗斯轰炸行动中的防空能力发出警告，强调爱国者系统的必要性。尽管面临平民伤亡和基础设施损坏，泽伦斯基仍然对美国国会的支持抱有希望，并对各种援助方案持开放态度。俄罗斯边境附近的冲突凸显了国际援助的紧迫性。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:15:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraines-zelenskiy-warns-of-air-defence-shortage-amid-russian-attacks/articleshow/109095807.cms</guid></item><item><title>艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统：以色列正在进行“血腥而艰难的战争”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-fighting-bloody-and-difficult-war-president-isaac-herzog/articleshow/109095574.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095574.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统强调了冲突的严重性，因为以色列面临着六个月的里程碑。人质尸体的打捞和针对总理内塔尼亚胡管理的抗议活动增添了阴沉的基调。哈马斯袭击造成 1,170 人伤亡，人质仍被扣押在加沙。以色列的军事反应影响到平民，凸显了持久的冲突。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 22:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-fighting-bloody-and-difficult-war-president-isaac-herzog/articleshow/109095574.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国机构：导弹险些击中也门港口西南方向的船只</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/missile-narrowly-misses-vessel-southwest-of-yemeni-port-uk-agency/articleshow/109095509.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095509.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一枚导弹险些击中也门荷台达附近的一艘船只，但船员没有受伤。以美国为首的联军拦截了一枚导弹，另一枚则落入水中。胡塞叛军与以色列、英国和美国等国家之间的冲突不断升级。胡塞武装领导人承认伤亡并誓言瞄准红海航运。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/missile-narrowly-misses-vessel-southwest-of-yemeni-port-uk-agency/articleshow/109095509.cms</guid></item><item><title>南佛罗里达州酒吧发生致命枪战，造成2人死亡、7人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/deadly-gunfight-at-south-florida-bar-leaves-2-dead-7-injured/articleshow/109095376.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095376.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;佛罗里达州多拉市一家酒吧发生致命枪战，造成两人死亡、七人受伤。顾客之间的冲突升级，导致一名保安被枪杀。多拉尔警察与袭击者交火，导致枪手死亡。调查正在进行中，以确定事件背后的动机。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/deadly-gunfight-at-south-florida-bar-leaves-2-dead-7-injured/articleshow/109095376.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯呼吁对“危险的”外德涅斯特无人机袭击事件进行调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-calls-for-investigation-into-dangerous-transdniestria-drone-attack/articleshow/109095357.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095357.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯批评无人机袭击了摩尔多瓦分离的外德涅斯特地区的一处军事设施，称这是出于对扩张担忧的挑衅。乌克兰军队击退了俄罗斯军队，缓解了人们的担忧。该事件引发了要求调查的呼声，德涅斯特河沿岸和摩尔多瓦处于高度戒备状态，凸显了地区紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:19:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-calls-for-investigation-into-dangerous-transdniestria-drone-attack/articleshow/109095357.cms</guid></item><item><title>蒙古9%的牲畜因冬季“dzuds”而损失</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/9-mongolia-livestock-lost-to-winter-dzuds/articleshow/109095350.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095350.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;气候变化加剧的极端冬季天气导致蒙古数百万头牲畜死亡，影响了严重依赖动物收入的游牧社区。联合国报告称，过去二十年来，蒙古的自然灾害增加了一倍，加剧了土地退化、荒漠化和水资源短缺，使牲畜在严冬中生存更加困难。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:15:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/9-mongolia-livestock-lost-to-winter-dzuds/articleshow/109095350.cms</guid></item><item><title>另一名印度学生在美国被发现死亡，引发担忧</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/concerns-spiral-as-another-indian-student-found-dead-in-the-us/articleshow/109095341.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095341.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;印度学生乌玛·萨蒂亚·赛·加德 (Uma Satya Sai Gadde) 在美国克利夫兰去世，引发社会担忧。印度领事馆正在调查此案，并努力遣返她的遗体。全球印度教传统基金会呼吁联邦调查局对美国印度学生死亡事件进行独立调查，并通过在线请愿书收集支持。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/concerns-spiral-as-another-indian-student-found-dead-in-the-us/articleshow/109095341.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称敌人将对叙利亚卫队的杀戮感到“遗憾”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-says-enemy-will-regret-guards-killings-in-syria/articleshow/109095337.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095337.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗警告称，七名革命卫队士兵在大马士革袭击中丧生后，伊朗将进行报复。德黑兰誓言要对其大使馆领事馆附件进行报复，袭击目标是七名伊斯兰革命卫队成员。应对措施将是战略性的，以产生最大的影响。参谋长的讲话凸显了伊朗对抗对手的决心。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-says-enemy-will-regret-guards-killings-in-syria/articleshow/109095337.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙发现一名人质尸体，停火谈判将恢复</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-finds-the-body-of-a-hostage-killed-in-gaza-while-talks-will-resume-on-a-cease-fire/articleshow/109095326.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095326.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列军方在加沙找到了一名被扣为人质的 47 岁农民的尸体，随着谈判恢复，以色列军方加大了释放剩余人质的压力。据信，这名农民埃拉德·卡齐尔 (Elad Katzir) 被伊斯兰圣战武装分子杀害，家人敦促在冲突造成的毁灭性损失中迅速采取行动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-finds-the-body-of-a-hostage-killed-in-gaza-while-talks-will-resume-on-a-cease-fire/articleshow/109095326.cms</guid></item><item><title>维珍飞机机翼夹住一架停在希思罗机场的英航飞机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/virgin-aircraft-wing-clips-a-parked-ba-jet-at-heathrow/articleshow/109095321.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095321.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一架维珍大西洋航空公司的飞机在希思罗机场与一架英国航空公司的飞机相撞。没有人员受伤的报道。维珍航空的波音 787-9 撞上了一架静止的飞机。希思罗机场和航空公司迅速做出反应。维珍正在进行调查和维护检查。两家航空公司都保证航班不会受到干扰。希思罗机场确认没有乘客受伤或运营受到影响。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 20:58:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/virgin-aircraft-wing-clips-a-parked-ba-jet-at-heathrow/articleshow/109095321.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯导弹袭击乌克兰 造成8人死亡、12人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-missile-strikes-in-ukraine-kill-8-and-wound-12/articleshow/109095313.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095313.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯对乌克兰的导弹袭击造成8人死亡、12人受伤，对居民区和基础设施造成严重破坏。袭击针对哈尔科夫和敖德萨地区，据报道有平民伤亡。乌克兰军队拦截了多枚导弹和无人机，而俄罗斯军方则声称成功击中了军事目标。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 20:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-missile-strikes-in-ukraine-kill-8-and-wound-12/articleshow/109095313.cms</guid></item><item><title>从 1994 年的恐怖到非洲的羡慕：卢旺达统治者牢牢掌控</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/from-the-1994-horror-to-the-envy-of-africa-rwandas-ruler-holds-tight-grip/articleshow/109095310.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109095310.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 1994 年，卢旺达面临毁灭性的种族灭绝，但今天，基加利成为非洲进步的中心。该市拥有现代化的基础设施，举办重大活动，也是旅游热点。卡加梅总统的领导受到威权主义的批评，推动了经济增长和发展，但种族紧张局势持续存在，影响着卢旺达的未来。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 20:51:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/from-the-1994-horror-to-the-envy-of-africa-rwandas-ruler-holds-tight-grip/articleshow/109095310.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>